{"tid":1041821,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"低等人類應該要裝返個倒後鏡","createTime":"2019-03-01T06:30:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T08:39:28.000Z","uid":129013,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dec185222953a94eaaeb69b6da65b0c65ed29a40","tid":1041821,"uid":129013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T06:30:15.000Z","msg":"特別係啲蝗同蝻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一係就出左扶手電梯企正喺個出口位度搵路塞住後面啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一係就行行下突然停低，後面如果停唔切就實撞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再唔係就企喺班馬線出入口位，綠燈唔行塞喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再再唔係就喺只夠2~3人行嘅路孖住咁行，塞q住晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n強烈要求強國同各蝻國幫佢地啲國民人體改造，裝返個倒後鏡畀佢地，等佢地識得望下佢地身後，造福下世人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9646f2efca72d8dccffc06c5db4cd882d584b64","tid":1041821,"uid":221571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T06:31:58.000Z","msg":"停低咪照撞埋佢<br />\n大條道理屌鳩佢添呀"},{"pid":"7c10acdc4c9f158eb20243ffa3f697795e2f4ce9","tid":1041821,"uid":129013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9646f2efca72d8dccffc06c5db4cd882d584b64","tid":1041821,"uid":221571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T06:31:58.000Z","msg":"停低咪照撞埋佢<br />\n大條道理屌鳩佢添呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T06:33:37.000Z","msg":"舍身撞擊，自己都會痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a944f6493b3f06793121a3f903599e4d09ba3bd","tid":1041821,"uid":221571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c10acd